/*
 * experiments.cpp — All 8 PQSCAAS benchmarking experiments.
 *
 * Faithfully reproduces pqscaas_experiment_v2/experiments/exp*.py.
 * TEE operations are REAL SGX ECALLs measured with chrono.
 * PQ crypto uses calibrated lognormal mock (matching Python MOCK_LATENCY_MS).
 * AEAD/SHA-256 use real OpenSSL on the untrusted side.
 */

